        "id": 12525,
        "name": "Paul Adamson",
        "username": "padamson",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.foundationdb.org/padamson/{size}/1420_2.png",
        "created_at": "2023-03-08T12:12:19.702Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This seems to work <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/twitter/eyes.png?v=12\" title=\":eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eyes:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-auto\"> processes:\n    general:\n      customParameters:\n      - memory=20GiB\n      - knob_storage_hard_limit_bytes=10GiB\n      - knob_target_bytes_per_storage_server=9GiB\n</code></pre>\n<p>which seems to be correctly interpreted into the commandline which I can see from the operator logs:</p>\n<pre data-code-wrap=\"none\"><code class=\"lang-plaintext\">/usr/bin/fdbserver \n--class=log \n--cluster_file=/var/fdb/data/fdb.cluster \n--datadir=/var/fdb/data \n--knob_storage_hard_limit_bytes=10GiB \n--knob_target_bytes_per_storage_server=9GiB\n...```</code></pre>",
